{"tid":2075676,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[港台電視] 有種人生 逢星期六 2130-2200","createTime":"2020-06-23T04:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T14:45:18.000Z","uid":30,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a6c39ec482baa508a95d74393747aaf8578af8","tid":2075676,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T04:14:32.000Z","msg":"有種人生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/103619835_4552079384817433_6729138784235235051_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=jiB1f7H9_ksAX_TqnnN&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=16627463c106cdcfaaf1f70dda3e235e&amp;oe=5F16E9A8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F103619835_4552079384817433_6729138784235235051_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DjiB1f7H9_ksAX_TqnnN%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D16627463c106cdcfaaf1f70dda3e235e%26oe%3D5F16E9A8&h=58bd1032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人生如耕種，沒有付出就沒有收穫。然而，在香港這個事事追求最大利益的地方，若希望收穫豐盛，耕種在芸芸行業中似乎都不是最佳選擇，可是為何近年越來越多香港人喜歡耕種呢？從耕種中，可以感受到什麼喜悅？令人生有什麼改變？<br />\n<br />\n看似無可避免。但喺密布嘅高樓之中，係咪仲有容納大自然嘅空間？<br />\n<br />\n#雲耕一族 社企負責人徐伽（Andrew）聯同幾位拍檔，同唔同機構合作，善用市區一啲被遺忘嘅空間發展成農圃，達致城鄉平衡。園圃亦令弱勢人士發揮所長，例如熱愛種植嘅聽障人士Eva，就喺農圃中搵到自己嘅人生方向。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=63YdCcwKcK4&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR2oQs_0PjNRp9Nq18A7tOHRHIlGd30-F55-NuePp7ihxrObxIy_YDnd6Bk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D63YdCcwKcK4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26fbclid%3DIwAR2oQs_0PjNRp9Nq18A7tOHRHIlGd30-F55-NuePp7ihxrObxIy_YDnd6Bk&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7lDf25aqCgCAAhwKlvpwqyI%3D&h=0f7c37a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=63YdCcwKcK4&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR2oQs_0PjNRp9Nq18A7tOHRHIlGd30-F55-NuePp7ihxrObxIy_YDnd6Bk</a>"},{"pid":"1e7c6d9f23135802a13383f873e90ca54548f59b","tid":2075676,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"有種人生   第一集: 今生無悔   04/07/2020<br />\n<br />\n在湖南郴州有一個橙園，極目遠望，連綿數個山頭，面積超過二萬畝。對一般人來說，它是一個足足有六分一個香港島那麼大的農場，但對身為香港人的園主來說，這可能是他人生最後的一個挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n今年69歲的李道德在香港土生土長，九十年代開始在內地設塑膠廠，原本衣食無憂，十年前卻因參加了一個步行長征的慈善活動，邊走過黃土荒涼的山丘，邊萌起經營果園的念頭。李道德除了希望種出高質素的臍橙，還要求建立一個保持土地潔淨、可持續發展的模式，更期望有日可將橙園交給慈善團體，利用盈餘幫助別人。<br />\n<br />\n可是，挑戰遠比想像中多。多年來投資巨額金錢，花上十年光陰，橙園距離收支平衡卻仍有一段距離。他的家人、朋友、下屬，又如何看待這位永不言悔的老人家？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/farmingmylife/originals/mfile_8931_685208_1_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Ffarmingmylife%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8931_685208_1_l.jpg&h=ea96f162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/farmingmylife/originals/mfile_8931_685208_2_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Ffarmingmylife%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8931_685208_2_l.jpg&h=01a14a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/farmingmylife/originals/mfile_8931_685208_6_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Ffarmingmylife%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8931_685208_6_l.jpg&h=084aea1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/farmingmylife/originals/mfile_8931_685208_3_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Ffarmingmylife%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8931_685208_3_l.jpg&h=ee63215f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f126c804de19f02f58a1e9fe1b6f7d1dcdd3e101","tid":2075676,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T04:17:10.000Z","msg":"有種人生．前奏曲 : 復耕本土米<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2CQfksBJXZI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2CQfksBJXZI&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7lDf25aqCgCAAhwKlvpwqyI%3D&h=e858ff2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2CQfksBJXZI</a><br />\n香港出產的元朗絲苗曾經揚威海外，雖然現已成為傳說，但至今仍有人希望復興本地米。<br />\n自小在元朗農村長大的楊俊武(Mole)，近年引入廣西絲苗的種子於牛潭尾復耕，希望一代一代地留種，多年後可以種出真正的本地絲苗。作為半農半職農夫，Mole將所有工餘時間都投放在農田，希望透過復耕農地，守護自己成長的地方。<br />\n<br />\n主持:梁祖堯<br />\n資料撰稿:李紫欣<br />\n編導:張育堅<br />\n監製:唐敏明"},{"pid":"1b989fe1e5dc549814b2384e1abdae9b0d71a99c","tid":2075676,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T15:31:44.000Z","msg":"原來有post 推下先"},{"pid":"09edcb82afbb6a67bbfc40f32e6f2c63a516cc4d","tid":2075676,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T15:31:59.000Z","msg":"第一集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lfM4UYINvWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlfM4UYINvWE&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7lDf25aqCgCAAhwKlvpwqyI%3D&h=9f11602c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lfM4UYINvWE</a>"},{"pid":"1f3f79def7ce505f39643149c3f144aeec86fac5","tid":2075676,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09edcb82afbb6a67bbfc40f32e6f2c63a516cc4d","tid":2075676,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T15:31:59.000Z","msg":"第一集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lfM4UYINvWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlfM4UYINvWE&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7lDf25aqCgCAAhwKlvpwqyI%3D&h=9f11602c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lfM4UYINvWE</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"大陸種冇乜興趣"},{"pid":"3ba8fd9315cca3ff3ac64d8bb69001c81cfb9b2f","tid":2075676,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f3f79def7ce505f39643149c3f144aeec86fac5","tid":2075676,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score